node.text:
Our moment of choice is at hand. There has never been a more urgent moment for humanity to come together in synergy and collectively choose to hold the greatest vision of what we can be and do together, to lead with our hearts and co-create new possibilities that will offer us hope for our future.
This uplifting and timely book with 43 of the world's brightest evolutionary leaders is a call to action, offering evolutionary visions, resources and practical steps to help us navigate this moment of choice and amplify the movement for global transformation, upon which our future depends.

Get your copy of Our Moment of Choice here: https://bit.ly/ourmomentofchoice #OurMomentOfChoice #OMOM #Choice #GreggBraden #WisdomTraditions

node.text:
It's not a secret that our world is changing. Change isn't always easy, especially when you haven't been prepared for the kinds of changes that we are experiencing today. My goal is to help you embrace change in a healthy way so you can move forward with more resilience and confidence. 

That's why I created my all-new online course Radical Resilience that begins on Monday, July 13, 2020.

During this course, I will guide you through the new discoveries, the rock-solid science, and the proven techniques, to create powerful resilience in every aspect of your life. You'll experience six 60-minute workshops, where you will learn how to awaken and maintain resilience in your life! PLUS! you'll get to join me for three LIVE 30-minute Q&A forums.

If you're interested in joining me you can learn more and register at the link in my Bio or go to www.radicalresilience.greggbraden.com

I look forward to spending the next 3-weeks with you and sharing this information that I know will help you through all of life's challenges. #radicalresilience #resilience #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions 

#RadicalResilience #resilience #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions

node.text:
People tell me all the time that they want to change the world. The question is: How?

Realistically, what can we do as individuals in the face of so many simultaneous crises? How can we turn our time of extremes into a time of transformation? And how do we share our personal transformation with our communities and loved ones?

I've designed my newest course to help with exactly that. I'm excited to share that it is now available in both English and Spanish. Link is in my Bio. 

If you are asking yourself if this is the right course for you, here are four facts I would invite you to consider:

Fact 1: Now is different. From the realities of climate change to the breakdown of social norms and politics, a convergence of conditions unlike anything known in the past is upon us. It’s because now is different that the thinking of the past no longer works to solve our problems.

Fact 2: Life gets better, and resilience is the key. Personal resilience makes room for big shifts in our lives, and is our greatest ally in our time of extremes.

Fact 3: We already have the solutions we need. We already have the solutions to the big issues that face us today and we need to build the “road” of thinking that gives the “wheel” of solutions something to travel upon.

Fact 4: The biggest crisis is the most difficult to accept—It’s a crisis in thinking. We must embrace the thinking that allows us to accept the existing solutions into our lives.

It’s these four facts that cut to the very heart of what we’re up against and hold the keys to the next step of transformation, both for ourselves and for the world. Our ability to thrive in the midst of such massive change—our personal resilience—is the first step to ensure the success of our journey.

So, here is the chance to make room for new possibilities and positive change in your life.

Be a part of Radical Resilience and change the way you respond to the world.

#radicalresilience #radicalresilienceonlinecourse #resilience #greggbraden #wisdomtraditions
